  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Capital Ships are the largest type of military ship. Th=
ey
  have unmatched offense and defense.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>They can carry multiple troops for planetary invasion. =
They
  also typically have area weapons</span>, such as HyperDeny components that
  prevent enemy ships from escaping to hyperspace.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>To supply the high power requirements of their heavy
  weaponry, Capital Ships usually have multiple reactors.<o:p></o:p></span>=
</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>While large and heavily armed, they are are slower and =
less
  agile than smaller ships like frigates.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Capital Ships often serve as the lead ship for a fleet.=
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
